whats
---------

whats is a tool to quickly look up something from the command line,
written in Go.


How to build
------------

$ make

move whats to any location in your $PATH. eg: /usr/local/bin


How to run
----------

$ whats <something>

example:

$ whats love

Love is a variety of different feelings, states, and attitudes that ranges from 
interpersonal affection ("I love my mother") to pleasure ("I loved that meal").
It can referÂ ...


How does whats work
-------------------

It's a client that uses a google search api. Then it make a naive
guess out of the results which one to choose, and displays the result
